Resume Analyzer App

An AI-powered Resume Analyzer that evaluates resumes and provides smart suggestions to improve job readiness and ATS compatibility.

---

 Features

* Resume parsing and information extraction
* Skill analysis and keyword matching
* ATS (Applicant Tracking System) compatibility check
* Smart suggestions for improving resume quality
* Score-based evaluation system

---

 Tech Stack

* Python
* NLP
* Streamlit 
     CSS (for UI)
---

 Installation

1. Clone the repository

```
git clone https://github.com/your-username/resume-analyzer.git
```

2. Navigate to project folder

```
cd resume-analyzer
```

3. Install dependencies

```
pip install -r requirements.txt
```

4. Run the application

```
streamlit run app.py

``
Output

Upload a resume → Get analysis → Improve your resume ✨

